data.description: Welcome to your new dream home in the highly sought-after Jones Mill Crossing neighborhood, nestled conveniently 5 minutes away from downtown Simpsonville and downtown Fountain Inn! This charming single level home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting three spacious bedrooms and two full baths, this well-maintained residence offers a practical and functional layout that is perfect for all styles of life. You will love the open floor plan, creating a seamless flow from the living room to the kitchen and breakfast area, making an ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The home is loaded with upgrades: granite countertops, shiplap and crown molding throughout - a large 2 car garage with additional storage area. Step outside to the fenced backyard featuring a large patio that is great for enjoying the outdoors and hosting gatherings with friends and family. Jones Mill Crossing is a neighborhood that has it all, featuring a community pool, beautiful walking trails and large common areas for activities. Located across the street from the prestigious Rudolph Gordon Elementary/Middle School residents are able to walk to school, and only several minutes away from the new Fountain Inn High School. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home.
